     9| *   4. Typed confirmation string ("DELETE" / "TRUNCATE" / "DROP").
    10| *   5. An immutable audit record.
    11| *
    12| * A destructive op is NOT executed until BOTH approvals are recorded. The
    13| * request creates a pending approval record; the second approver confirms it.
    14| *
    15| * @module ivx-two-person-approval
    16| */
    17|
    18|import { promises as fs } from 'node:fs';
